Monica Jacobs Birwinyo (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 4 n'ọnwa Juun n'afọ 1990) bụ onye Uganda na-eme ihe nkiri na onye igwe onyonyo

Ọ malitere ọrụ ya dị ka onye na-eme ihe nkiri na-amalite site na ọrụ ndị a na-edeghị aha ya ma na-aga n'ihu na ọrụ ugboro ugboro na Imbabazi, The Pardon na Irene Kulabako's Beauty to Ashes na NBS hit series Because of U
5@home, the Honorablez, Mela and Zansanze a egwuregwu ogbo

Na Machị na afo 2012, a kwadoro Monica Birwinyo, Irene Asumpta na Jacob Nsaali dị ka ndị na-akwado oge mbụ nke Movie Digest Show. Ugbu a, ya na Usama Mukwaya na-egosi oge nke abụọ. Monica gosipụtara na nso nso a na Joel Karekezi's Imbabazi, The Pardon, dị ka Muhoza
